  "reviews": [
    {
      "text": "Nick has done an excellent job on various projects in my house including installing a new flue, removing a gas fire and installing a downstairs toilet. Throughout all these tasks he's shown himself to be a thoughtful and capable engineer and adept at solving problems and coming up with creative solutions. He's got a wide range of skills which include putting up walls and doors, tiling and of course neat and tidy pipework.",
      "reviewer": "Tom",
      "rating": 5
    },
    {
      "text": "Really fantastic service. Nick has worked diligently on our bathroom and gone the extra mile when things were difficult to complete due to our apartment structure. He has worked without complaint when met with unpredictable obstacles and the finished job is excellent.  He has been respectful and tidy in his work throughout.\nI would highly recommend. Thanks Nick!",
      "reviewer": "Emma",
      "rating": 5
    },
    {
      "text": "Nick has done various bits of plumbing and heating work for us over the last few years. This has included boiler repairs, services, radiator installation and refitting and tiling a downstairs toilet. Everything has been completed to a really high quality and at a reasonable price. He is punctual, tidy, good at communicating and I would 100% recommend him.",
      "reviewer": "Michael",
      "rating": 5
    },
    {
      "text": "Nick helped fix a leak at very short notice. i had already contained the leak and was extremely worried about the reaction and proposal of another plumbing company I had come view the issue. Nick is very well mannered, calm and got on with the job quickly. I would definitely use him again to sort out any issues.\n\nJude",
      "reviewer": "Jude",
      "rating": 5
    },
    {
      "text": "I have been using Nick to do some work over the last year, after being let down by someone else. Nick is reliable, efficient, trustworthy and honest. Finding good tradespeople is great as it removes unnecessary stress. I would recommend Nick to anyone with plumbing and gas boiler problems.",
      "reviewer": "Justin",
      "rating": 5
    }
  ],
